Transactions HOWTO
Updated 04/20/02 by Rusty

This document will describe how to set up credit card and paypal payment processing in Scoop, for example to sell ads on your site.


CREDIT CARDS
------------

Currently the only credit card system accepted is Linkpoint's LPERL wrapper. For instructions on how to enable Scoop's Linkpoint capabilities, please see doc/Linkpoint.howto.
